Description: R6 classes for prototyping system dynamics models and a solver to
  simulate the initial value problem of first-order ordinary differential 
  equations (ODE) that specifies the model definition. A wrapper around the ode 
  solver from the deSolve-package. 
  Also supports static models and coupling to represent more complex systems. 
Depends:
  R (>= 2.15.0)
License: GPL
